summary: An ordinance accepting a deed from Dorseys, Inc., to portion of the southwest one-quarter of the southeast one-quarter and of the north one-half of the southeast one-quarter of the southwest one-quarter of Section 9, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W. M., for street purposes, and laying off East 47th Street, East 48th Street, East 49th Street and 24th Avenue Northeast.
